---
title: Squash Ravioli in Leek Sauce with Candied Walnuts
description: Pillowy soft butternut squash stuffed ravioli is tossed in a savoury leek and spinach sauce with a sprinkle of smoky candied walnuts for barely-there heat and sweet crunch!
